    {
      "_id": "sN3JKaIDG5kFRAvC",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
      "name": "Natural Camouflage",
      "sort": 400000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "gm": "",
          "value": "<p>A tatzlwyrm's green, gray, and brown scales provide it natural camouflage. In areas of dense undergrowth, a tatzlwyrm can move at its full Speed when @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.VMozDqMMuK5kpoX4]{Sneaking}, and it gains a +4 circumstance bonus to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.XMcnh4cSI32tljXa]{Hide}.</p>"
        },
